CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 16, 1961, pg. A3 reads: " 'New Era' Dawns at Herron Hill Junior High - Keys In Program - The social studies team is shown in an impromptu meeting. Left to right: Leo M. Rautekus, student leader of Duquesne University; Miss Julia L. Battles, Robert Nicklos, Eugene G. Khorey, team leader, and John R. Young."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Herron Hill Junior High School social studies team, left to right: Leo M. Rautekus, Julia L. Battles, Robert Nicklos, Eugene G. Khorey, and John R. Young, standing against two toned wall
